library(shiny)
library(ggplot2)
library(colourpicker)
#library(shinythemes)
library(glue)
library(shinyjs)

shapes = read.csv("shape.csv")
#_______________________________________________________________________________
#                   UI
#~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

ui <- 
    fluidPage(
        #themeSelector(),
        titlePanel("Faithful Data exploration"),
        # Histogram with controls..............................................
        sidebarLayout(
            sidebarPanel(
                # Select Variable for Histogram
                selectInput(
                    inputId = "select_var",
                    label   = tags$p("Select Variable",
                                     style="font-size: 20px; color:grey50"),
                    choices = list("Eruption Time"="eruptions",
                                   "Waiting Time" ="waiting"),
                    selected = "eruptions",
                    selectize = T, multiple = F,width ="150px"
                ),
                # Histogram Settings,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
                tags$p("Histogram Settings",style="font-size: 20px; color:grey50"),
                fluidRow(
                    ## 1. Histogram color
                    column(6,colourpicker::colourInput(
                        inputId = "hist_col",
                        label   = "Color",
                        value   = "black", 
                        allowTransparent = TRUE, returnName = TRUE,closeOnClick = TRUE
                    )),
                    ## 2. Histogram Fill
                    column(6,colourpicker::colourInput(
                        inputId = "hist_fill",
                        label   = "Fill",
                        value   = "lightblue", 
                        allowTransparent = TRUE, returnName = TRUE,closeOnClick = TRUE
                    )),
                ),
                ## 3. Histrogram Bins number slider
                sliderInput(inputId = "bins",
                            label   = "Bins",
                            min = 2, max = 50,value = 30),
                ## Add some empty spaces
                br(), br(), br(), br(), br(), br()
             
            ),
            mainPanel(
                plotOutput(outputId = "hist"),    # render histogram
                br(),
                verbatimTextOutput(outputId = "summary") # render summary output
            )
        ),
        br(),
        # End of Histogram area ................................................
        
        # Scatterplot with controls ............................................
        sidebarLayout(
            sidebarPanel(
               checkboxInput(
                   inputId = "show_scatter",
                   label   = "Show Scatterplot",
                   value   = FALSE
               ),
               conditionalPanel(
                   condition = "input.show_scatter == true", #Condition for showing below items
                   hr(),
                   h4("Density Line Settings"),
                   ### Start of one Fluid Row --------1-------------------------------------------
                   fluidRow(
                       ## Density Line Width
                       column(8,sliderInput(
                           inputId = "line_slide",
                           label   = "Line Width",
                           min = 0.05, max = 7,value = 1, step = 0.05
                       )),
                       ## Density Line Color
                       column(4,colourpicker::colourInput(
                           inputId = "line_col",
                           label   = "Color",
                           value   = "darkgreen",
                           allowTransparent = TRUE, returnName = TRUE,closeOnClick = TRUE
                       ))
                   ),
                   ### End of Fluid Row ------------1-------------------------------------------
                   ## Point Size
                   sliderInput(
                       inputId = "point_size",
                       label   = "Point Size",
                       min =0.5,max = 10,value = 6,step = 0.5
                   ),
                   ### Start of one Fluid Row -------2--------------------------------------------
                   fluidRow(
                       ## Density Line Width
                       column(6,colourpicker::colourInput(
                           inputId = "point_col",
                           label   = "Color",
                           value   = "#14006652",
                           allowTransparent = TRUE, returnName = TRUE,closeOnClick = TRUE
                       )),
                       ## Density Line Color
                       column(6,
                           # colourpicker::colourpicker::colourInput(
                           #     inputId = "point_fill",
                           #     label   = "Fill",
                           #     value   = "darkgreen",
                           #     allowTransparent = TRUE, returnName = TRUE,closeOnClick = TRUE
                           # )
                           uiOutput(outputId = "point_fill_ui")
                       )
                       
                   ),
                   ### End of Fluid Row -------------2--------------------------------------------
                   ## Point Shape
                   radioButtons(
                       inputId = "shape",
                       label   = "Select Shape",
                       choiceNames = shapes$symble, 
                       choiceValues = shapes$value,selected = 16,inline = T
                   )
               )
            ),
            mainPanel(conditionalPanel(
                condition = "input.show_scatter == true", #Condition for showing below items
                plotOutput(outputId = "scatterplot"))
            )
        )
    )


#_______________________________________________________________________________
#                 SERVER
#~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

ser <- function(input,output,session){
    
    
    # Histogram Generation ................................................
    output$hist <-renderPlot({
        var_name = ifelse(input$select_var=="eruptions","Eruption","Waiting")
        var_mean = mean(faithful[[input$select_var]],na.rm=TRUE)
        var_sd   = sd(faithful[[input$select_var]],na.rm=TRUE)
        ggplot(faithful, aes(x = get(input$select_var))) +
            geom_vline(xintercept = var_mean,
                       color="darkgreen", size=2.5, alpha=.5)+
            geom_vline(xintercept = var_mean-var_sd,
                       color="grey23", size=2, alpha=.3)+
            geom_vline(xintercept = var_mean+var_sd,
                       color="grey23", size=2, alpha=.3)+
            geom_histogram(
                mapping =  aes(y = after_stat(density)),
                bins    = input$bins,
                fill    = input$hist_fill,
                color   = input$hist_col
            ) +
            geom_density(aes(y = after_stat(density)),
                         alpha = 0.3,
                         fill = input$hist_fill
            ) +
            labs(
                title = glue(
                    "Histogram and Density Plot of {var_name} time"
                ),
                 x = glue("{var_name} Time (mins)"),
                 y = "Density"
            ) +
            theme_minimal()+
            theme(title =element_text(size=18))
    })
    
    # Summery Generation .......................................................
    output$summary <- renderPrint({
        x = faithful[[input$select_var]]
        round(c(summary(x),"SD"=sd(x)),3)[c(1:3,5,6,4,7)]
    })
    
    # Manual Point Fills UI Render  ...................................................
    output$point_fill_ui <- renderUI({
        if (as.numeric(input$shape) %in% 21:25){
            colourpicker::colourInput(
                inputId = "point_fill",
                label   = "Fill",
                value   = "darkgreen",
                allowTransparent = TRUE, returnName = TRUE, closeOnClick = TRUE
            )
        } else {
            NULL
        }
    })
    
    # Scatterplot Generation ...................................................
    
    output$scatterplot <- renderPlot({

        v =c("Eruption","Waiting")
        #var = ifelse(input$select_var=="eruptions",v[c(1,2)],v[c(2,1)])
        if (as.numeric(input$shape) %in% 21:25) {
            point_fill = input$point_fill
        } else {
            point_fill ="black"
        }

        ggplot(faithful, aes(eruptions, waiting)) +
            geom_density2d(linewidth  = input$line_slide,
                           color      = input$line_col) +
            geom_point(color = input$point_col, 
                       fill  = point_fill,
                       shape = as.numeric(input$shape),
                       size  = input$point_size)+
            labs(title = glue("Scatterplot of {v[1]} Vs {v[2]} time"),
                 x = glue("{v[1]} Time (mins)"),
                 y = glue("{v[2]} Time (mins)")) +
            theme_minimal()+
            theme(title =element_text(size=17))
    })
    
    
}    # end of server function

#______________________________________________
#                 APPLICATION
#~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

shinyApp(ui,ser)
